gw.lang.reflect

Class PropertyMethodFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.lang.reflect.PropertyMethodFinder

  • public class PropertyMethodFinder
extends java.lang.Object
    Helps improve performance and memory management for property method access. For example, iterating over Class.getMethods() is quite slow and requires a fresh copy of all a class's methods.
